    "content": "<!--Línea informativa-->\n<div style=\"align-items: center; color: #555555; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; font-size: 1rem; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">\n  <span>📅 <b>Última revisión:</b> 9 de agosto 2025</span> | \n  <span>📌 <b>Estado:</b> <span style=\"color: #c62828; font-weight: 600;\">🔴 No iniciado</span></span> | \n  <span>🏨 <b>Ámbito:</b> <span style=\"color: #045a91;\">Cumbria Spa&hotel</span></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEifBt4g1lKAhnX7539yjo6QX4Uja-BNJ4janDNGju-kJuWhfkL6w-hQcHOYMLuITZZPRyXxA5yJLYnnz4cps_PEQQEoUabvv8z2zpu6d3pe6TQYTfp808uflj0WG7j1BBBe7kETPz8BX-BFWqEB6XSuGfVl9WiumBuNnuRNYkVetUKsvxcpu6RfeElm2oq2/s703/logo-synergy-.png\" style=\"display: block; padding: 1em 0; text-align: center; \"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" width=\"320\" data-original-height=\"242\" data-original-width=\"703\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEifBt4g1lKAhnX7539yjo6QX4Uja-BNJ4janDNGju-kJuWhfkL6w-hQcHOYMLuITZZPRyXxA5yJLYnnz4cps_PEQQEoUabvv8z2zpu6d3pe6TQYTfp808uflj0WG7j1BBBe7kETPz8BX-BFWqEB6XSuGfVl9WiumBuNnuRNYkVetUKsvxcpu6RfeElm2oq2/s320/logo-synergy-.png\"/></a></div>",
